import { ally, enemy } from "../dataSet";

export const unit1 = {
    id:null,
    level:4,
    unit:1,
    name:"Melee infantry",
    team:ally,
    maxHp:100,
    hp:100,
    damage:100,
    width:100,
    height:100,
    location:null,
    createTime:1,
    upperBody:"대기",
    lowerBody:"대기",
    hitRange:40,
    attackRange:40,
    attackSpeed:(40 * 20),
    preDelay:(40 * 6),
};
export const unit2 = {
    id:null,
    level:4,
    unit:2,
    name:"Infantry",
    team:ally,
    maxHp:100,
    hp:100,
    damage:100,
    width:100,
    height:100,
    location:null,
    createTime:1,
    upperBody:"대기",
    lowerBody:"대기",
    hitRange:40,
    attackRange:200,
    attackSpeed:(40 * 18),
    preDelay:(40 * 2),
};
export const unit3 = {
    id:null,
    level:4,
    unit:3,
    name:"Tank",
    team:ally,
    maxHp:200,
    hp:200,
    damage:100,
    width:100,
    height:200,
    location:null,
    createTime:1,
    upperBody:"대기",
    lowerBody:"대기",
    hitRange:200,
    attackRange:200,
    attackSpeed:(40 * 26),
    preDelay:(40 * 8),
};
